                            <h1>Green Energy Marketplace</h1>
                            <p>A marketplace for green energy solutions tailored to agricultural needs, such as solar powered
                                irrigation systems, wind turbines for farms, and biogas energy solutions.
                            </p>
                            <p><a class="btn btn-lg btn-primary" asp-controller="Product" asp-action="Create">Add New Product </a></p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="carousel-item c-item">
                    <img src="~/style_extra/s5.jpg" class="d-block w-100 c-img" alt="Slide 3"> <div class="container">
                        <div class="carousel-caption text-end">
                            <h1>Educational and Training Resources</h1>
                            <p>
                                Online courses, webinars, and workshops on integrating green energy technologies in
