      <div class="col-md-7 order-md-2">
            <h2 class="featurette-heading fw-normal lh-1  bg-custom">
                Government Grants for Agroforestry Initiatives.
                <span class="badge badge-sm rounded-pill badge-custom">
                    Funding Opportunity
                </span>
            </h2>
            <p class="lead">Are you a farmer interested in integrating trees into your agricultural landscape to enhance biodiversity, soil health, and crop resilience? Look no further! Various government agencies are offering grants and subsidies specifically tailored to support agroforestry initiatives.</p>
        </div>
